These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant
House: palace, tower
City: london, nizza
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
2. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
3. the tower house is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | blueberry  | eggplant   |
| House   | tower     | palace   |
| City         | nizza | london |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
House: cottage, farmhouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, tiparillo
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
2. the pall-mall-smoker is the person driving the tram##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| House          | cottage     | farmhouse |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | pall-mall  |
| Sport           | parkour         | lacrosse     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, surfing
City: rome, london
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Sport    | surfing     | parkour |
| City         | london | rome    |
| Color         | chestnut         | ivory        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, malaysian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling
1. the malaysian is on the right of the polish##1
2. the nurse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Job          | nurse   | entrepreneur  |
| Nationality         | polish | malaysian     |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | cycling         |

