The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, engineer
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, fishing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the engineer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport      | swimming | parkour       |
| Job           | engineer      | dancer     |
| Hobby   | fishing       | traveling   |
| Cigar           | swisher          | chaman |

