.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the dutch##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Birthday           | july | march    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Flower           | zinnia         | tulip    |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy    | scientific   |

