The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, skydiving
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
