House: tower, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet         | goat   | horse |
| Birthday           | january | september    |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | indie         |
| House         | tower   | art-deco |

